{"tid":2122157,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國奧斯卡遊戲獎項評分標準太過在意角色背景？官方：希望藉此推動更多樣化的社會","createTime":"2020-07-23T22:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T00:39:55.000Z","uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0ebac74c86e800d0781f5340449eab9d3e11f21e","tid":2122157,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:13:58.000Z","msg":"《最後生還者2》所鬧出的爭議風波讓玩家們激起了非常多的討論，有許多人就認為劇情上太過政治正確，強調女權主義等元素太過頭了。而也因此有的玩家族群開始對宣揚所謂「政治正確」理念的部分遊戲或劇情感到反感，認為這些事情太過頻繁出現而且沒必要，今 (23) 日有網友於 PTT 上 PO 出 2021 年英國奧斯卡獨立出來的遊戲獎項 BAFTA 的評分標準，再度引起了熱烈的討論<br />\n<br />\n根據 2021 年 British Academy of Film and Telvision Arts (BAFTA) 中<span class=\"red\">「最佳英國遊戲」的評分標準，遊戲的性別比例必須差不多、且至少 10% 角色是 LGBTQ+ 族群身分，7% 是殘障人士、20% 的少數族裔，此外也有角色出身要是低社會階層的角色、主線支線任務等也被限制必須要與低社會階層有所關係</span>，被許多網友質疑是否管太寬了，反而忽略了其他部分。<br />\n<br />\n然而該獎項的官方新聞稿中也有指出，他們希望這個獎項能夠幫助處於經濟不利背景的人以及其他較弱勢的族群發聲，並提升整體環境的多樣性，而現實的情況是 LGBT 族群不論在社會上還是遊戲作品中仍然處於較少數的存在，BAFTA 希望透過這些評分標準從遊戲中提升遊戲的「多樣性」，進而影響到現實社會，當人們在遊戲中對少數族群見怪不怪，那麼在現實社會中或許也能接納彼此，創造更好的社會環境。<br />\n<br />\n評分標準PDF<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bafta.org/sites/default/files/uploads/baftabfidiversitystandardsforgames2021pilot.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bafta.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fuploads%2Fbaftabfidiversitystandardsforgames2021pilot.pdf&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6E%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=ede7d667\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bafta.org/sites/default/files/uploads/baftabfidiversitystandardsforgames2021pilot.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來源<br />\n<a href=\"https://games.yahoo.com.tw/bafta-135452580.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgames.yahoo.com.tw%2Fbafta-135452580.html&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6E%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=b2b124f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://games.yahoo.com.tw/bafta-135452580.html</a>"},{"pid":"35987f3cc61af356ec526db7b51f8f053d6411bb","tid":2122157,"uid":75969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:14:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gUooUk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gUooUk.png&h=faebc709&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eccead32c2795ddd573e7781ee15dfb5801db795","tid":2122157,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:15:34.000Z","msg":"BAFTA同奧斯卡有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bcf5713875ccae9e462df4e31f2f22a8b7dd81a","tid":2122157,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eccead32c2795ddd573e7781ee15dfb5801db795","tid":2122157,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:15:34.000Z","msg":"BAFTA同奧斯卡有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:18:51.000Z","msg":"英國電影學院獎（英語：British Academy Film Awards）又稱英國影藝學院電影獎（英語：BAFTA Awards），是由英國電影和電視藝術學院頒發的一年一度的英國電影、電視藝術相關產業最高表彰，其地位、權威性與公信力相當於美國的奧斯卡獎，所以中文世界媒體有時會直稱英國奧斯卡獎（英語：British Oscar）<br />\n<br />\n應該係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4200a3d57222090274ea1d8b6817584ad2e0f8bf","tid":2122157,"uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:19:32.000Z","msg":"且至少 10% 角色是 LGBTQ+ 族群身分，7% 是殘障人士、20% 的少數族裔<br />\n<br />\n唔怪得艾莉最尾要斷手指<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39543ede6f66376805e1e7034fa0c2529ef0776f","tid":2122157,"uid":194326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:20:33.000Z","msg":"forced love = rape"},{"pid":"0949739e42f37fb0b19c22c3e1a2c1d4a3a1beaf","tid":2122157,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T22:21:46.000Z","msg":"左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"right\"><span class=\"medium\"><strong>[⇩ 美國形勢大好⇩]</strong></span><br />\n<span class=\"small\">- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/pAcortX\" data-auto-link 